flowchart TD
    A[Input .dl8 dataset] --> B[Train/test split]
    B --> C[Adaptive binning / threshold extraction]
    C --> D[Candidate predicate generation]
    D --> E{Language-specific search}
    E --> E1[1D]
    E --> E2[Horn]
    E --> E3[AntiHorn]
    E --> E4[ConjUI\n(empirical auxiliary)]
    E --> E5[Square2CNF]
    E --> E6[Affine\n(empirical auxiliary)]
    E --> E7[BestPN\n(empirical by default)]
    E1 --> F[Information gain / penalized gain scoring]
    E2 --> F
    E3 --> F
    E4 --> F
    E5 --> F
    E6 --> F
    E7 --> F
    F --> G[Best split selection]
    G --> H[Recursive tree construction]
    H --> I{Stopping criteria met?}
    I -- No --> D
    I -- Yes --> J[Learned MDT]
